## Fans

* **GET** /app/:key/fans/
* **GET** /app/:key/fan/:email
* **POST** /app/:key/fan
* **PUT** /app/:key/fan/:email
* **DEL** /app/:key/fan/:email

```
{
  _id: @_id,
  name: @name.full,
  email: @email,
  social: @social,
  api: {
    key: @api.key
  },
  notifications: @notifications,
  groups: @groups,
  info: @info
}
```